We could use a new section type for this, e.g. `BufferFormatCheck.export`, and put function signatures in there that we could parse, e.g.
```c
/////////////// BufferFormatCheck.export ///////////////

const char *__Pyx_BufFmt_CheckString(__Pyx_BufFmt_Context*, const char*);
void __Pyx_BufFmt_Init(__Pyx_BufFmt_Context *, __Pyx_BufFmt_StackElem *,const __Pyx_TypeInfo *);
```
Looks more readable to me.

